{
  "stem": "26111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in order to do that, he had to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We stayed there for two years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And afterwards, we-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] till '38-- and in early-- middle of '38, we moved to a more modest place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Much smaller than his other practice had been, much less lucrative.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, the only restriction on ones-- I mean, there were many restrictions about entry to professions, entry to universities, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But once you were-- once you had all that, you had your education, you had your profession.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The one restriction that I can-- [LAUGHS] that I can remember is since the Nazis had this obsession about the, the, the race-- about the, the 'rapist race.' Jews were-- their dearest wish was to-- was to rape or to have intercourse with non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jewish women weren't of that much interest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the other was a-- was a kind of a victory over the Aryan race.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, driven by this obsession, in 1935-- and I'm sure you know this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was quite well-publicized abroad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Party Congress passed a regulation that in no Jewish-- no Jewish household must employ any household help, employee that is less than 45 years-- female that is less than 45 years old.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They figured at 45 years old, [LAUGHS] nobody would want-- not even the rapacious Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had a lady working for us that was quite a bit more than 45, and a very dear, dear person.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was full of hope at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And don't forget, this was in '36.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were [SIGHS] many, many Jews still that thought this would pass.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
